@Add a port for Locale::Maketext::Simple. From DESCR:

This module is a simple wrapper around Locale::Maketext::Lexicon,
designed to alleviate the need of creating "Language Classes" for module
authors.
@
text
@# $MirOS: ports/devel/p5-Algorithm-Annotate/Makefile,v 1.1 2007/09/15 22:34:57 bsiegert Exp $

